This is the administration interface for MHC-PMS apotheker application.
It used the Python based Django application framework. The interface is auto-generated
from the database.

Install following Software:
* Python 2.7
* PIP
* virtualenv
* Python MySQL Driver (mysqldb)

E.g. Debian/Ubuntu:
sudo apt-get install python-pip python-virtualenv python-mysqldb

Open a terminal/cmd and enter following commands:
 cd <your projects>/ch.bfh.bti7081.s2013.blue/admin-src
 virtualenv ../admin-venv
 source ../admin-venv/bin/activate # ..\admin-venv\Scripts\activate on Windows
 pip install -r requirements.txt
 python manage.py syncdb

From now on, to start the server you have to do:
 source ../admin-venv/bin/activate # ..\admin-venv\Scripts\activate on Windows
 python manage.py runserver

The application is now accesible under http://localhost:8000/admin/ 
